## 5. Gap analysis vs sales use case

| Requirement | Today | Gap |
|-------------|--------|-----|
| Framework-aware coaching (MEDDPICC, SPIN) | Interview HUD tags | No first-class **stage model**, **coverage scoring**, or **playbook objects** |
| Prep → live continuity | Session-local state; KB JSON | No durable **session store**, **deal object**, or **versioned playbook** |
| Multi-agent | Profiler + Copilot only | No **supervisor**, **router**, or **specialists** (objections, pricing, security, demo script) |
| Multi-model | One provider per deployment | No **task routing** (e.g. GPT-class vs Claude vs local classifier) |
| Structured output | Markdown-ish sections | No enforced **JSON schema** / tool calls for machine-verifiable steps |
| Latency isolation | Sequential SSE | Profiler + copilot can **block perception** of responsiveness |
| Compliance / CRM | N/A | No integration hooks; future agents must design **audit logs** and **data residency** |

